---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <CategoryHero
    title={title}
    description={description}
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611001897293-561e0c30f938"
  />

  <article class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-16">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600">
        Santorini's sunsets are world-renowned, painting the white-washed buildings and caldera in golden hues.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Prime Photography Locations</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      {photoSpots.map(spot => (
        <PhotoSpot {...spot} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Photography Tips</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {photographyTips.map(tip => (
        <PhotoTip {...tip} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Essential Information</h2>
      <h3>Best Times to Visit</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>April-May for mild weather and fewer crowds</li>
        <li>September-October for warm seas and clear skies</li>
        <li>Blue hour (after sunset) for balanced lighting</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Equipment Recommendations</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Wide-angle lens (16-35mm)</li>
        <li>Medium zoom (24-70mm)</li>
        <li>Neutral density filters</li>
        <li>Polarizing filter</li>
        <li>Sturdy tripod</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Alternative Viewpoints</h3>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Location</th>
            <th>Best For</th>
            <th>Crowd Level</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Fira Trail</td>
            <td>Walking shots, caldera views</td>
            <td>Moderate</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Santo Wines</td>
            <td>Sunset with wine tasting</td>
            <td>High</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Akrotiri Lighthouse</td>
            <td>Southern panoramas</td>
            <td>Low</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <blockquote>
        <p>"Santorini's sunsets are not just a daily event, but a celebration of light, color, and architecture that photographers dream of capturing."</p>
      </blockquote>

      <h3>Local Tips</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Book a sunset cruise for unique perspectives from the water</li>
        <li>Visit popular spots during sunrise for fewer crowds</li>
        <li>Consider rooftop restaurants for unobstructed views (with dinner reservation)</li>
        <li>Use the walking trails between towns for unique vantage points</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>